  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together mildly spicy sauce, jamaican jerk seasoning, olive oil, paprika, garlic powder, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add chicken, onion, and bell pepper to the bowl, and toss to coat.",
    "Thread chicken and vegetables onto skewers, leaving a little space between each piece.",
    "Grill skewers for 8-10 minutes, turning occasionally, or until chicken is cooked through.",
    "Brush with olive oil during the last 2 minutes of cooking.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
